ass=\"reference-text\">I. Ousby ed., <i>The Cambridge Guide to Literature in English</i> (1995) p. 245</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Quoted in M. H. Abrams, <i>The Mirror and the Lamp</i> (1971) p. 332</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-14\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">S. Chatterji, <i>Memories of a Lost War</i> (2001) p. 70</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-15\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-15\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">W. B. Yeats, <i>The Poems</i> (1984) p. 155</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-16\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-16\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://call-for-papers.sas.upenn.edu/node/33792\">Tools of the Sacred</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1283\nCached time: 20180830191551\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.060 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.071 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 388/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 2254/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 923/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 4681/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.004/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 657 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   35.225      1 -total\n 70.66%   24.889      1 Template:Columns-list\n 61.33%   21.602      1 Template:Div_col\n 29.10%   10.249      1 Template:Reflist\n  9.03%    3.180      2 Template:Column-width\n  6.77%    2.383      3 Template:Main_other\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in